莫屬 如毒癮<br />\n只知活著原來為合一<br />\n喘泣 喘泣 慾望如何說不<br />\n看身軀抖震<br />\n<br />\n想獻奉 想對望 想贖回 <br />\n想下回<br />\n<br />\n伸出我的舌尖遊走過百合<br />\n讓舌尖必經我的眼中留下過足印 深深嵌<br />\n太多東西失去了吧但仍然呼吸<br />\n再多東西一念無明仍偶然哭泣<br />\n非你就莫屬 願十年如一日<br />\n<br />\n開了嗎 白泛桃紅百合<br />\n愛的花蓓"},{"pid":"557f06480124dceaf4dd428ba808aba77c9ce6fd","tid":239323,"uid":26878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T14:32:49.000Z","msg":"痛快間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又痛又快<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aecbd606c20489f5b87422ba14522c1a6f4f9d8d","tid":239323,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T15:07:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>痛快間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又痛又快<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搞掂晒喇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9a5b9263a58ee222a48d7b7e6218881b4393d9","tid":239323,"uid":53825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T15:08:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>lm 改呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢改慣改熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\